From 3aa4998c6b963242f1f01ddd025e7fe866e795aa Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sean <sean@cangaroo.ai>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 12:38:03 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Add animations and design updates from Figma notes

- Hero: Ken Burns slow zoom/pan animation on hero image
- Hero: Alpha "A" logo overlay with fade-in (acnestudios reference)
- Hero: "Stone.Life. Style." tagline section below hero
- Landing: "Natural stone depth" middle CTA section linking to collections
- Landing: Gallery images now link to about page anchor points
- Collections: Slab pan animation on collection swatch images
- Product pages (52): Slab pan animation on full slab images
- Product pages (52): Subtle zoom on hover for close-up swatch images
- All animations respect prefers-reduced-motion

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
